            Please note: Descriptions such as compulsive gambling, gambling addiction, gambling as a form of 
												mental illness, gambling as a type of disease, gambling as a disorder, adversity caused by gambling losses, 
												pathological gambling, and irresponsible gambling all are commonly accepted descriptions used to describe problem 
												gambling.